| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0340 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3ef0e0f9-dac6-5c70-b51b-cdcd59be72c1"
